714
00:54:29,587 --> 00:54:31,722
- Assisti tudo.
- Bom.

715
00:54:32,700 --> 00:54:34,365
Inclusive a sua parte.

716
00:54:36,530 --> 00:54:39,242
- Isso era Top Gun?
- Sim, era.

717
00:54:44,373 --> 00:54:46,677
